ygData.messageBody:
Congrats Faras. You are truly one of the better bards on E'ci. One thing
really stuck out in your log. Both Faras and Galtin were born on the same
day:-) Of course he is still stuck at 39th level and will likely remain
there. Having a newborn who requires frequent diaper changes is not
condusive to playing EQ.

Galtin of E'ci
